channel.title: Pre-Workshop Tasks :: Kentik Partner Workshop
channel.description: Prior to this workshop, you should have received an email with instructions on how to set up a free trial Kentik account. This is a prerequisite step in order to be able to run the Labs during the workshop. If you already have registered for an account you can follow the tasks for validation. Task 0.1 - Register for a Free Trial Account Navigate to kentik.com/get-started and fill in your details in the form to create your free trial Kentik account.
